snippet.title: A5 - A Ressha de Ikou 5 PSX Game Opening movie
snippet.description:
Opening movie of the PS1 game A5   A Ressha de Ikou 5 a fine strategy game.

Intro del juego de PS1 A5   A Ressha de Ikou 5, un buen juego de estrategia.
